{"tid":2283384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有親戚得左肺癌第三期 我應唔應該同老母講呢隻病得少於五年命","createTime":"2020-11-12T13:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T18:32:14.000Z","uid":58841,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"18b72bda4f30133bb44a08d6c04d7599c2efa65d","tid":2283384,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"姨丈最近驗左有肺癌第三期<br />\n佢有兩個仔女<br />\n個仔去左美國做野<br />\n個女去左加拿大讀書<br />\n老母同我講姨丈無講呢隻病俾仔女知<br />\n但係姨丈已經行唔到路<br />\n我應唔應該勸老母話呢隻病得返少於五年命<br />\n再唔講我驚對仔女見唔到老豆最後一面<br />\n我聽到已經爭啲喊埋出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca056a02444385472b7a452c6252ef10ad588635","tid":2283384,"uid":37796,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"人知道幾時死唔係全然壞事<br />\n梗係叫佢地見埋最後一面<br />\n唔好留遺憾 真係要博盡無悔<br />\n<br />\n以前我個姨婆同我地一齊住(五六十年代黎香港)<br />\n後尾佢中肺結核<br />\n個陣我仲係小學<br />\n佢入左醫院之後就冇出返黎 見唔到最後一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d97e44e86b577f0e4afe59879fd1661a6ae965","tid":2283384,"uid":49211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"年紀大可能得返一兩年 當然要講"},{"pid":"b8a4c51529cc0504321fdbb9d234422e17758b17","tid":2283384,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"46d97e44e86b577f0e4afe59879fd1661a6ae965","tid":2283384,"uid":49211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"年紀大可能得返一兩年 當然要講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"只係40幾50歲<br />\n唔食煙 酒就間中先飲<br />\n唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3982d68e86ad136bbb52ce03d2fafcb3a152d401","tid":2283384,"uid":271431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"緊係講啦.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" clas